{"tid":1731154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大同學不要亂： 被困校內不等於犯了法!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-11-17T16:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T16:33:16.000Z","uid":34773,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aae36b8ce74af300ccb8ffc6ef5b311e9a80624a","tid":1731154,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"【緊急廣傳】<br />\n理大同學不要亂：<br />\n被困校內不等於犯了法，<br />\n請各同學不要絕望不要做傻事。<br />\n就算警方最後入校拘捕所有人，<br />\n不等於警方可以在毫無疑點的基礎下，<br />\n證明在校內拘捕的每一個人都犯了暴動罪等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n扮被困, 燒晒裝備!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"f4a69f944923abcee32c6168b24b74613a6edc75","tid":1731154,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e46b0e89ef207a31b663cb762fedeeb81bc9871","tid":1731154,"uid":282496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7f5e3ec0280016c03d12fb44b71099d0840f9f","tid":1731154,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"根本就係被困 點扮"},{"pid":"10a5146af9e2848ba35c6799e6b1db1b8745fd95","tid":1731154,"uid":294869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1a7f5e3ec0280016c03d12fb44b71099d0840f9f","tid":1731154,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"根本就係被困 點扮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"想想：  離開poly俾人拉，法律上係poly入面並非犯罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 想想：  離開poly俾人拉，法律上係poly入面並非犯罪<br />\n<br />\n【傳比係poly嘅朋友】<br />\n剛剛收到律師係法律上嘅建議，<br />\n比起而家離開poly比人拉，<br />\n 法律上係poly入面並非犯罪，<br />\n喺入面嘅人可以road機拍自己 U life生活有幾平靜 ，<br />\n睇書睇電視點都好。 <br />\n之後如果強行俾人拉咗，<br />\n呢啲都會係辯方證據。<br />\n<br />\n一群學生在自己學校裏面，<br />\n一齊念經。<br />\n那是一個宗教集會，<br />\n他們沒有戴口罩，<br />\n他們有犯法嗎?<br />\n<br />\n警方強攻入大學拉人，<br />\n始終比在校外拉人更加難睇，<br />\n 世界上看來仍然是闖入大學校園。<br />\n<br />\n看來學生應該留在校內，<br />\n不要作任何非法行為，<br />\n應該更安全。<br />\n<br />\n假若學生全部換曬平常衣服，<br />\n坐在自己學校裏通宵查看聖經，<br />\n沒有犯法。<br />\n留在校內，不是更加安全嗎?"},{"pid":"c0479ece51c8f9372177b3934d22291516237037","tid":1731154,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"急，推: 理大人手足舉美國旗，大聲唱美國歌啊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"979827b28d0b278aecf11efc7f71ce846e7257b7","tid":1731154,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"瞓咗幾耐<br />\n唔打死你都偷笑"},{"pid":"7eb34d0a43592b428fd2c914cfafd362e973e8b5","tid":1731154,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"979827b28d0b278aecf11efc7f71ce846e7257b7","tid":1731154,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"瞓咗幾耐<br />\n唔打死你都偷笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"你係咪想入面啲手足做傻事你先安樂"}]}